author: Ryan Daws
description:
An in-depth look at the software development industry from JetBrains shows that AI skills are now fundamental for developers. JetBrains’ Developer Ecosystem Survey has been charting the industry’s evolution since 2017. For its 2025 edition, JetBrains gathered responses from over 24,500 developers worldwide and found a profession juggling new tools, new pressures, and a new […]

The post AI skills now vital, but software developers say people matter most appeared first on Developer Tech News.
title: AI skills now vital, but software developers say people matter most
